snippet.title: Grimvalor - Launch Trailer (iOS)
snippet.description:
Grimvalor is now available on the App Store! https://itunes.apple.com/us/app/grimvalor/id1369179088?ls=1&mt=8

Also available on Google Play:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.direlight.grimvalor

Find out more about the game on our website at: https://direlight.com/grimvalor/
